				<li id="16600976" class="cmnt-root" data="56" data-d="1649315066000"><ul class="comments"><li class="comment-box"><div class="avatar"><img src="/images/avatar.png" alt="" /><div class="comment-username">Anonymous</div></div><div class="comment"><div class="title"><span class="txt-subject"></span><input style="display: none;" class="txt-subject-ed"><span class="right cmt-ui"><a href="https://fextralife.com/forums/t579232/Torchpole" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">07 Apr 2022 03:04</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class="report-post" href="https://fextralife.com/forums/report.php?f=193&p=16600976" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" title="report this post"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-flag" aria-hidden="true"></span></a></span></div><p class="txt-comment">Some Highlights i&apos;ve had with this weapon as i&apos;ve used it purely all the way to the capital so far.<br/><br/>It&apos;s a light source, has long reach and uses the spear moveset which most npc enemies struggle to avoid and space.<br/>It&apos;s a fire weapon which seems to be strong verse beasts and causes unique burn animations on Giant hands and plants that disable them and give them a DoT<br/>The fire animation is effective at tracking invisible enemies<br/>The light attack sometimes hits through walls ,especially when jumping<br/>Charged strong attacks cause you to run forth and lunge, great for hit and run as you prepare someone for a stagger.<br/>Charged strong attacksalmost always instantly stun bats.<br/>Charge Forth will knock over almost all humanoids(Didn&apos;t work on a misbegotten beast though).<br/>I&apos;ve never seen anyone else use this weapon, you feel pretty unique in coop running around with it.<br/>Spears in general are painful for invaders to deal with.<br/><br/>Despite the perks, you do have to put a lot more effort into it to fight enemies and the dps in general is a lot lower than most weapons that would have status effects on them and just scale better. jump attacks on this aren&apos;t the best and you&apos;ll have to use careful strong attacks and charge forths to make this shine. <br/></p><textarea style="display: none;" class="txt-comment-ed"></textarea><div class="clearfix"><a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#zz-16600976" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Reply</a><a id="btnExpandComment" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#replies-16600976" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Replies (<span class="replies">0</span>)</a><div class="vote pull-right"><section class="t-up"><span></span><p>56</p><i class="add">+1</i></section><section class="t-down"><span></span><p>0</p><i class="sub">-1</i></section></div></div><div class="collapse-com transparent"><div class="col-trigger collapse" id="zz-16600976"><div class="ng-scope"><textarea id="dcomment" class="ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-invalid ng-invalid-required" placeholder="Input your comments:"></textarea><button id="btn-16600976" class="btn btn-default btnPostReply"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-pencil"></i> Submit</button><img id="newCommentAvatar" src="//fextralife.com/forums/download/file.php?avatar=73284_1520393011.png"/></div></div></div></div><div class="clearfix"></div><ul class="children collapse" id="replies-16600976"></ul></li></ul></li>
			
